[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うりゃーーーっ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00304",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "よいしょ、っと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00305",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うわ、二人ともつっよ……\n援護なんていらなかったかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00306",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "クレオの剣は竜巻みたい……\nあっちのお姉さんは、雷……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00307",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "クレオ姫のは軍隊仕込みの１対多を想定した剣術、\n彼女のは１対１を即座に仕掛け続ける剣術ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00308",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まとめて倒すか、１体ずつ速攻で倒すか……\n強さの中にも、その人らしさが出るんだ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00309",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ありがとう助かっちゃった！　初めての無数島群域に\n浮かれすぎて、つい奥地まで冒険しちゃったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00310",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私は冒険者のメーヴェ・シュテルネンリヒト。\n舌噛んじゃうだろうから、メーヴェって呼んで！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00311",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "分かりました、メーヴェさん。\nアタシはアルビーナ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00312",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（んん？　シュテルネンリヒトって、\n　レスナと同じ……？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00313",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "私はヤンネで、この子がベップよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00314",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "よろしく、雷のお姉さん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00315",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "もう、そんな恥ずかしいよ。お姉さんなんて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00316",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "雷のほうはいいんだ。\nあ、私はクレオ・ランターナ、よろしくね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00317",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "クレオ・ランターナ……ってあの王女様の？\nロマンさんからこっちにいるって聞いてないんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00318",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "リヒャルト兄さんのこと知ってるの？\nほんと兄さん、顔だけは広いんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00319",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うん。王都に戻った時、ロマンさんに雇われてね。\nこっちにいるレスナに手を貸してやってほしいって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00320",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、やっぱり！　そのレスナって、１に錬金術、\n２に錬金術、３に錬金術のあのレスナっすか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00321",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "錬金術しか印象ないん、かーーーいっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00322",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "でもそうね、確かにうちの子は錬金術大好きだわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00323",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "つ、つまり、あなたはレスナのお母さん！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00324",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ええ。その様子じゃうちの娘のこと知ってるのね。\nあの子ったら、すっかり有名人なんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00325",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "レスナママ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00326",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ふふふ、\nメーヴェお姉さんって呼んでくれてもいいのよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00327",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "若々しくて羨ましいわ。私の子がレスナちゃんくらいに\n大きくなった頃には、きっと私はヨボヨボよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00328",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そんな～、ヤンネさんだっけ？　あなたもとっても\n若々しくて素敵よ～？　肌のお手入れは何をしてるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00329",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（井戸端会議が始まった……これは長くなるぞ……\n　それにしても）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00330",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（レスナのお母さんか……\n　レスナとは違う方向性で綺麗な人だな……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00331",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ・シュテルネンリヒト",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen Sternenlicht",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "冒険者の女性。\nとある人を探して、世界中を一人で旅している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]